short_summary: The Department of National Defence has a requirement for Nozzle Assemblies, Tank Washing for CFB Halifax, Nova Scotia and CFB Esquimalt, British Columbia.
description: This is a Request for Proposal (RFP) to procure two types of Nozzle Assemblies, which are NSN: 01-156-8503. This is in accordance with the Government of Canada’s Expenditure Management Framework. The Equipment is to be supplied to the Canadian Armed Forces. Bidders proposing an Equivalent or a Substitute Product must indicate the brand name and model and/or Part Number and the NCAGE they are offering.
